--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Result
   Output: (o_totalprice + '1'::double precision), (o_totalprice - '1'::double precision), (o_totalprice * '1'::double precision), (o_totalprice / '1'::double precision)
   ->  Seq Scan on public.orders
         Output: o_totalprice
         Filter: ((orders.o_orderkey = 1000) AND ((orders.o_shippriority + 1) > 10))
 Optimizer: pg_orca
(6 rows)

